################################################################################
# FCGames — fluxo completo de ponta a ponta
#
# Use com a extensão "REST Client" (VS Code) ou o HTTP Client (Rider/IntelliJ).
# Clique em "Send Request" acima de cada bloco, na ordem. Token e IDs são
# encadeados automaticamente entre as requisições (não precisa copiar nada).
#
# Pré-requisito: docker compose up (stack completa no ar).
# Acompanhe os efeitos em: docker compose logs -f notifications-worker
################################################################################

@users = http://localhost:5001
@catalog = http://localhost:5002
@payments = http://localhost:5003
@notifications = http://localhost:5004

### 1) Cadastra um usuário  → dispara UsuarioCriadoEvento
#    (catalog cria biblioteca vazia; notifications loga "email-boas-vindas")
# @name cadastro
POST {{users}}/usuarios
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Maria",
  "email": "maria@teste.com",
  "senha": "Maria@123"
}

### 2) Login  → retorna o token JWT
# @name login
POST {{users}}/usuarios/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "maria@teste.com",
  "senha": "Maria@123"
}

@token = {{login.response.body.token}}
@usuarioId = {{cadastro.response.body.id}}

### 3) Lista os jogos (seed)  → veja os IDs/preços retornados
# @name jogos
GET {{catalog}}/jogos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# Seed: Hades 49,90 / Hollow Knight 29,90 (Aprovados) | Cyberpunk 2077 149,90 (Rejeitado).
# A ordem do array pode variar — confira o resultado de #3 e ajuste os índices abaixo se preciso.
@jogoAprovado = {{jogos.response.body.$[0].id}}
@jogoRejeitado = {{jogos.response.body.$[2].id}}

### 4) COMPRA APROVADA (Hades 49,90)  → 202 + orderId
#    → pagamento Aprovado → pedido Aprovado + item na biblioteca
#    → notifications loga "email-confirmacao-compra"
# @name compraAprovada
POST {{catalog}}/compras
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jogoId": "{{jogoAprovado}}"
}

### 5) COMPRA REJEITADA (Cyberpunk 2077 149,90 > 100)
#    → pagamento Rejeitado → pedido Rejeitado (sem item na biblioteca)
#    → notifications loga "email-pagamento-rejeitado"
# @name compraRejeitada
POST {{catalog}}/compras
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jogoId": "{{jogoRejeitado}}"
}

### 6) Consulta o pedido aprovado  (aguarde 1-2s após #4 — processamento é assíncrono)
#    Se o campo do id não for "orderId", veja a resposta de #4 e ajuste.
GET {{catalog}}/compras/{{compraAprovada.response.body.orderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7) Consulta o pagamento correspondente
GET {{payments}}/pagamentos/{{compraAprovada.response.body.orderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8) Biblioteca do usuário  → deve conter Hades, não conter Cyberpunk
GET {{catalog}}/biblioteca/{{usuarioId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

################################################################################
# Fluxo de Admin (jogos são [Authorize Admin])
# Admin seedado: admin@fcgames.com / Admin@123
################################################################################

### Login do admin
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{users}}/usuarios/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@fcgames.com",
  "senha": "Admin@123"
}

### Cria um novo jogo (somente Admin)
POST {{catalog}}/jogos
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Stardew Valley",
  "descricao": "Fazendinha relaxante",
  "preco": 24.90
}

################################################################################
# Health checks
################################################################################

### users
GET {{users}}/health

### catalog
GET {{catalog}}/health

### payments
GET {{payments}}/health

### notifications
GET {{notifications}}/health
